Class MBTileFetcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • android.os.HandlerThread
        • com.mousebird.maply.SimpleTileFetcher
          • com.mousebird.maply.MBTileFetcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TileFetcher, java.lang.Runnable

    public class MBTileFetcher
extends SimpleTileFetcher
    MBTiles tile fetcher.
    This tile fetcher focuses on a single MBTiles file. You mate this with a QuadImageLoader to do the actual work.
    Will work for image or vector MBTiles files.
